{"tid":1008129,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[留港消費] 安順旅遊停業　明日起出發18團約570名旅客受影響","createTime":"2019-02-04T09:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T09:43:36.000Z","uid":64345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0ec428dc3cde5f53c944dc39bcc83b579567cb03","tid":1008129,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1441479-20190204.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1441479-20190204.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ%2BUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=2b523973\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1441479-20190204.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f30f2e77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1441479-20190204.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n旅遊業議會表示，下午收到安順旅遊有限公司通知，由即日起停止營業，約18個原定由明日起前往內地的中、短線旅行團將會取消，總共涉及約570名旅客和90多萬元的團費，當中包括原定於年初一至年初四期間出發的13個旅行團，涉及約430名旅客。<br />\n<br />\n至於已於昨日出發的桂林4天高鐵團則不受影響，30多名團員將於行程結束後返港。<br />\n<br />\n旅議會引述安順旅遊表示，由昨日起逐一通知受影響的旅客，所有旅行團的收據上均已蓋上印花，經電話報名的旅客亦已於付款後收到印花收據的相片，旅行社在取得旅客的地址後，會寄出收據正本。<br />\n<br />\n旅議會說，損失外遊費的旅客，若符合申請資格，可獲相等於所損失外遊費90%的特惠賠償。有關申請賠償事宜，旅客可由2月8日起聯絡旅遊業賠償基金秘書處，電話為31517945。<br />\n<br />\n截至下午4時，旅議會共收到5宗求助，涉及20名旅客，涉及團費約共21600港元，全部持有印花收據的正本或副本。"},{"pid":"0a3ad505492f76293a0ed895abae8a2c1087e17f","tid":1008129,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eaf7d78c955cc2bf936a187844792f1049e1155","tid":1008129,"uid":125357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}